<RadzenText TextStyle="TextStyle.Subtitle1" TagName="TagName.P" class="rz-pb-4">
    Group content with collapsible support.
</RadzenText>

<RadzenText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body1" class="rz-mb-8">
    Use <code>&lt;HeaderTemplate &gt;</code>, <code>&lt;ChildContent &gt;</code> and <code>&lt;SummaryTemplate &gt;</code> to define custom content for Panel component parts. Use <code>AllowCollapse</code> property to allow expand/collapse and <code>Expand</code> and <code>Collapse</code> callbacks to catch if Panel component is expanded or collapsed.
</RadzenText>
